{
  "stem": "294.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the meantime, the-- I think at the very beginning of the ghetto-- you know, my memory is not so hot either now anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to go out to that factory every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were being brought back by-- by the Germans-- by the SS-- back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But later, we didn't go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We worked within the ghetto, inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible, because-- first of all, you know, I'm not talking already about the food and the living conditions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One doesn't know how one can get acclimated to certain situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the fear of deportations-- because they arranged every few months when you didn't expect it-- you expected the-- the least, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- the-- they-- they told you to gather on a-- on a square.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, in one part of-- part of the ghetto was a special place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they then they did to the right and to the left, whoever they please.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mostly, older people and children were taken, in-- even in those early days of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And only the people with the work permit could stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In those days, we didn't, but there were starting to be rumors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very soon, about early 1942, when the deportations were more frequent-- and I understand that some people were able-- like one man they were talking about was able to flee, to escape from Belzec, you know.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was telling the stories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Belzec was like Majdanek, like Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a death camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not a work camp or, you know, where you could work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was specifically a death camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but nobody believed this man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
